{"type":"assistant.message","data":{"messageId":"a26395bf-d715-44fc-b588-87a3a6099b86","content":"`.testsettings` files are **not supported** by modern MSTest (v3+). You need to migrate to a `.runsettings` file. Here's what your file configures and how to migrate each part:\n\n| `.testsettings` setting | `.runsettings` equivalent |\n|---|---|\n| `TestTimeout = 30000` | `<TestTimeout>30000</TestTimeout>` in `<MSTest>` |\n| Code Coverage data collector | `<DataCollector>` in `<DataCollectors>` |\n| `AssemblyResolution` / `useLoadContext` | No longer needed (modern test host handles this) |","toolRequests":[{"toolCallId":"toolu_vrtx_01LgS6qjbLJubjNjgdPdnYPY","name":"report_intent","arguments":{"intent":"Creating .runsettings migration"},"type":"function"},{"toolCallId":"toolu_vrtx_01Gq3AU1JKRdv2jv4h4SQjhK","name":"create","arguments":{"path":"/tmp/sv-34b72884adc14eb694c9b7fa292b9b9e/local.runsettings","file_text":"<?xml version=\"1.0\" encoding=\"utf-8\"?>\n<RunSettings>\n  <MSTest>\n    <TestTimeout>30000</TestTimeout>\n  </MSTest>\n  <DataCollectionRunSettings>\n    <DataCollectors>\n      <DataCollector friendlyName=\"Code Coverage\"\n                     uri=\"datacollector://Microsoft/CodeCoverage/2.0\"\n                     assemblyQualifiedName=\"Microsoft.VisualStudio.TraceCollector.CoverageCollectorDataCollector, Microsoft.VisualStudio.TraceCollector, Culture=neutral\">\n        <Configuration>\n          <CodeCoverage />\n        </Configuration>\n      </DataCollector>\n    </DataCollectors>\n  </DataCollectionRunSettings>\n</RunSettings>\n"},"type":"function","intentionSummary":"create a new file at /tmp/sv-34b72884adc14eb694c9b7fa292b9b9e/local.runsettings."}],"interactionId":"53981b9f-9dea-4aac-a616-16b27fe3330e","reasoningOpaque":"","reasoningText":"The user has a `.testsettings` file (legacy format) and has upgraded to MSTest 3.8.0. The `.testsettings` format is no longer supported by modern MSTest. They need to migrate to a `.runsettings` file.\n\nLet 